OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCladding: Developers told  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto act on lower-height     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbuildings                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The housing secretary has said he will 
OL,6, be "absolutely willing to use legal    
OL,7, rules" to make builders pay for the    
OL,8, removal of unsafe cladding from        
OL,9, lower-height buildings.                
OL,11,FMichael Gove has written to firms,     
OL,12,Fgiving them until March to agree a plan
OL,13,Fto protect leaseholders trapped in     
OL,14,F"unsellable homes".                    
OL,16,FSo far, residents in blocks 11-18m high
OL,17,Fhave been ineligible for government    
OL,18,Fsupport to remove unsafe cladding.     
OL,20,FIt has left many with crippling bills. 
